dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Iron County, Wisconsin in 2019.[TYPE is defined as:CHECKED = A field-checked addressDRAWING = A point from an old (2007) set of mapsDRIVEWAY = The road-end of the drivewayGIS = Placed according to air photosUNKNOWN = A newly assigned address that doesn't have a structure to match to on the air photos]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
